data.description: $3,000 towards closing costs or rate buydown! Your choice! 2022 Solar Panels that you will own! New septic system coming soon! So many updates within the past 3 years. Modern kitchen with newer granite, cabinets, & stainless steel appliances. Your chef will love the cooks island to entertain & create at the same time! Newer tile floors & carpets throughout. Wait until you see the bathrooms- the primary offers a jetted shower experience like no other. Open & split floor plan for space and privacy. City water plus a water softener & reverse osmosis system.  Large back yard & private surroundings make this your own precious hideaway. Perfect location near shopping, dining, schools, & more. Quick jump to the beach or theme parks.
